### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/fleet/Azure.ResourceManager.ContainerServiceFleet/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/fleet/Azure.ResourceManager.ContainerServiceFleet/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 fleet` — injects snippet code from the new sample file into the README placeholder blocks. Verify the README diff shows populated code blocks.
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 fleet` — only needed if public types/members changed (they did in this push, but the API listing files were already regenerated by the AutoPR bot).
5. `dotnet format sdk/fleet/Azure.ResourceManager.ContainerServiceFleet/`

